\section NiftyMIDASPurpose Purpose

The NiftyMIDAS application was developed by the 
<a href="http://www.ucl.ac.uk/medical-image-computing">Centre For Medical Image Computing (CMIC)</a> to support
the work of the <a href="http://dementia.ion.ucl.ac.uk/">UCL Dementia Research Centre</a>.
NiftyMIDAS provides a variety of segmentation tools to provide atrophy measurements for clinical
trials.

NiftyMIDAS is not intended for clinical use.

